<p><span class="anchor" id="p25"></span><span class="c5">العدوى:</span> انظر ج‍ ١ ص ٢٥٧.<a href="#p25" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
